yopu must have a frame of referecne in which to illusion can kill you. In a
fantasy world, a plastic bag over the head illusion won't work, becuase no one
knows what plastic is, or that you can't breath through it.  a heart attack
might not work either, or a disease, due to lack of medical knowledge
