Well, IMHO, psychologically, anything is possible. I believe that every
illusion should have some chance of killing the patient, or why do we have
people who die in their sleep while having bad dreams. Otherwise, I would
think that the subconscious mind would/could cause the body to go into shock
or make the person pass out, etc because of what the conscious mind is/was
experiencing.

'General failure reading drive brain: (A)bort, (R)etry, (I)gnore?'

Dave
